---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "December 27, 2025";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - ClipQwik"
  description="Privacy Policy for ClipQwik - AI-Powered DaVinci Resolve Plugin"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 mb-8 transition-colors"
        >
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-purple max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            At ClipQwik (operated by Minim-l, LLC), we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our DaVinci Resolve plugin and related services.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            By using ClipQwik, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We collect minimal information necessary to provide our services:
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Email Address</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When you sign up for our beta program through our website, we collect your email address. This is the only personal information we collect during the signup process.
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">How We Store Your Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Email addresses collected through our beta signup form are stored securely in Google Sheets. We use Google's infrastructure to ensure data security and reliability.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We use your email address for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Send you beta program invitations and access instructions</li>
            <li>Provide important product updates and feature announcements</li>
            <li>Communicate critical security or service notifications</li>
            <li>Respond to your support requests or inquiries</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-white">We will never:</strong> Sell, rent, or share your email address with third parties for marketing purposes. We will not send you promotional emails without your explicit consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Storage and Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <li>Email addresses are stored in Google Sheets with restricted access</li>
            <li>Only authorized personnel have access to the beta signup data</li>
            <li>We use HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
            <li>Google Sheets access is protected by strong authentication measures</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Google Sheets</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We use Google Sheets as a data processor to store beta signup information. Google's use of this data is governed by their privacy policy. We have configured our Google Sheets implementation to minimize data exposure and maintain security.
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">No Tracking or Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our website does not use cookies, tracking pixels, or third-party analytics services. We do not track your browsing behavior or collect any usage statistics.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You have the following rights regarding your personal data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Access:</strong> You can request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Deletion:</strong> You can request that we delete your email address from our records</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Correction:</strong> You can request that we correct any inaccurate information</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Portability:</strong> You can request a machine-readable copy of your data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Opt-Out:</strong> You can unsubscribe from our emails at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@clipqwik.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">support@clipqwik.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We retain your email address for as long as necessary to provide you with beta program access and product updates. If you request deletion of your data, we will remove your email address from our systems within 30 days, unless we are required to retain it for legal compliance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">GDPR & CCPA Compliance</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We are committed to complying with applicable data protection regulations, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you are a resident of the European Union or California, you have additional rights under these regulations. Please contact us to exercise your rights or for any questions about our compliance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
              <strong class="text-white">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@clipqwik.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">support@clipqwik.com</a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              <strong class="text-white">Company:</strong> Minim-l, LLC
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
